498
00:38:49,990 --> 00:38:53,010
Do you really think we are ready for that?

499
00:38:56,540 --> 00:38:59,020
You forgot to take this.

500
00:38:59,960 --> 00:39:02,060
Thank you.

501
00:39:02,060 --> 00:39:04,720
Can I call you "sister"?

502
00:39:04,720 --> 00:39:07,010
