528
00:41:35,940 --> 00:41:39,730
If something goes wrong, a mere parents' meeting wouldn't make up for it.

529
00:41:39,730 --> 00:41:43,670
Okay, okay. Report, report.

530
00:41:47,100 --> 00:41:49,790
